task.summary: Default task
Created Guitar class and InstrumentType enum.
Added getter methods to Instrument class for brand, buyPrice and sellPrice.
Added guitar-specific properties to Guitar class, created IPlayable (with play() method) and ISellable (with calculateMarkup() method) interfaces.
Added Keys class with keys-specific properties and getters. Created a KeysType enum.
Added Drums class with basic methods.
Added Trumpet class with enum for Trumpet Types
Added Trumpet valves property.
Added Violin class with all methods.
Added SellableItem superclass, Accessory as a subclass, with InstrumentAccessory extending from it. Added enums for the type of accessory and the type of instrument accessory.
Added String description property to Accessory class.
Removed AccessoryType enum and property as unnecessary.
Removed AccessoryType enum and property as unnecessary.
Added SheetMusic class with title and pages properties.
Added Other class.
Refactored Instrument class to make it a subclass of SellableItem
Added Shop class with name (String) and shopInventory (ArrayList) properties.
Added method to add ISellables to shopInventory and to clear the inventory.
Added method to remove items from the shopInventory.
Added method to calculate total profit from shopInventory.
